list.item:
Quota Treatment: 

Group A—Frozen Salmon; Preserved Fish, Other, except
                                            Salmon; Apples and Pears; Common Woods; Nitrate of Soda;
                                            Radio Tubes; Silk Stockings; Patent Leather; Radios;
                                            Electric Domestic Refrigerators; Typewriters;
                                            Refrigerating Apparatus; Passenger Automobiles.

Group B—Preserved Crustaceans; Rolled Oats; Insulating
                                            Board; Automatic and non-automatic Electric Control
                                            Apparatus; Twist Drills, etc.; Circular Saws, etc.;
                                            Rubber Manufactures, others.
